Description: The Common Procurement Vocabulary (CPV) establishes a single classification system for public procurement aimed at standardising the references used by contracting authorities and entities to describe the subject of procurement contracts.The dataset created is comprised of CPV 2008 and CPV 2003 codes and the mappings between them.
